1
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:28,200
♪Confessing to the moon
in the rustling wind back then♪

2
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:34,440
♪Like a boat being swallowed up
among the cities♪

3
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:41,440
♪Watching the flowers fall in unease,
worries and troubles fill my mind♪

4
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:48,240
♪Am I going to where I want♪

5
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,960
♪To stay or to leave, you decide♪

6
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:54,960
♪Nations are different♪

7
00:00:55,280 --> 00:01:01,520
♪One without desire
is one that is not alive♪

8
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:04,560
♪Looking at the sky side by side♪

9
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:08,320
♪We've gotten closer with time♪

10
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:15,120
♪One glance,
the city of Chang'an is bare♪

11
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:22,360
♪Among the ridiculous people
and things is me♪

12
00:01:26,420 --> 00:01:30,390
=Dream of Chang'An=

13
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:32,950
=Episode 4=

14
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,760
(Now,)

15
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,720
(I'm sure that Cheng Ruoyu)

16
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,360
(is disappointed in me too.)

17
00:01:56,960 --> 00:02:00,220
(Royal Repository)

18
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,040
You are here, Little Fish.

19
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,000
How is it?

20
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,920
Did you find anything?

21
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:15,800
(Liu Juan)

22
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,800
We are too late.

23
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:18,960
What do you mean?

24
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,960
It means that

25
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,720
someone has cleaned up this place.

26
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,640
(Royal Repository)

27
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,760
Every book that is related

28
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,880
has been tampered with.

29
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:30,840
And he left no trace.

30
00:02:37,170 --> 00:02:38,350
(Guan Wu)

31
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,600
(Ren Cuilan)

32
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,240
Did you notice anything?

33
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,000
The ink inside

34
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,640
Zheng Wu's book

35
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,360
is different from others.

36
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,120
Resumes are often written in ink
from She Prefecture.

37
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,640
But it was sealed off by snow
on the 9th year of Tai'an.

38
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,640
We didn't get any ink
from them for two years.

39
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,280
So, the secretaries

40
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,640
had to use ink from Heng'an.

41
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,280
These two inks

42
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,080
are almost identical
in colours and shine.

43
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,640
The only difference is the smell.

44
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,880
This Resume of Zheng Wu
is written in the ink

45
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,280
from She Prefecture?

46
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,960
On the 10th year of Tai'an,

47
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,360
when you entered the palace,

48
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:24,080
this ink shouldn't have existed.

49
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,080
Is this the only one

50
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,280
with different ink?

51
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,400
Yours too.

52
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,080
Mine?

53
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,590
(Cheng Ruoyu)

54
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:47,450
(Guan Wu)

55
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,040
You found this?

56
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,960
Not me.

57
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,120
It's Qiu Yanzhi.

58
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,000
When I went to the Royal Repository
to investigate,

59
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,640
she was there too.

60
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,760
Why are you smiling?

61
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,040
Did you already know that

62
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,000
our Resumes

63
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,080
have been tampered with?

64
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,800
They are not tampered with.

65
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,560
These two books

66
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,520
are written afterwards.

67
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,560
Every six months,

68
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,240
Resumes will be put under the sun
to get rid of bookworms

69
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,640
and they'll be restored.

70
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,519
One time,

71
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,560
yours and Zheng Wu's book

72
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,600
were on top of each other.

73
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,960
And they were soaked in tea.

74
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:26,840
So, the secretaries

75
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,040
made another copy of them.

76
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,680
There's a record of this incident.

77
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,360
Didn't you see it?

78
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,600
No.

79
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,320
So, it means that

80
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,600
there's nothing wrong with my Resume.

81
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,400
Of course.

82
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,720
Not only yours,

83
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,240
but there's also nothing wrong
with Guan Wu's Resume too.

84
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,400
The problem started

85
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,560
before she entered the palace.

86
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,160
Not after.

87
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,320
Okay then.

88
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:49,640
Yu'er.

89
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,560
Don't get too close to Qiu Yanzhi.

90
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,400
Don't worry.

91
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,560
I have my boundaries.

92
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,640
Looks like they've found out about it.

93
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:09,320
Luckily,

94
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,760
we have a fail-safe.

95
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,960
In order not to make it obvious that

96
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,280
Yu'er's Resume is different,

97
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:17,200
we soaked the one below hers too.

98
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:20,040
And that happened to be Guan Wu's Resumes.

99
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,400
This is really fate.

100
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,600
As long as they don't investigate Yu'er,

101
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,560
everything will be fine.

102
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,520
I'm not worried about Yu'er.

103
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,480
I'm worried about Qiu Yanzhi.

104
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,080
A girl brought up by a cunning person

105
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:37,080
is indeed hard to deal with.

106
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,170
(On the first day of lunar January,
10th year of Tai'an...)

107
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,400
On the first day of lunar January
in the 10th year of Tai'an,

108
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,360
Emperor Wen rebuilt the Violet Bureau.

109
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:47,720
He chose 1000 people

110
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,960
and gave them 1000 bolts of silk

111
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,200
and 1000 koku of corns.

112
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,120
There were 1000 people?

113
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,160
But the Violet Bureau now

114
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,920
has only 36 maids.

115
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,640
Even if we include
the musicians and performers,

116
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,520
it'll just add up to 100.

117
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,560
Where are the rest?

118
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,360
They said that others were

119
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,320
asked to leave

120
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,440
after failing certain tests.

121
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,120
But according to the spies

122
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,160
I sent out to investigate,

123
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,640
a lot of them didn't go home.

124
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,120
They went missing?

125
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,560
This is the record of

126
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,240
His Majesty's hunting expenses
in recent years.

127
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,680
What do you see?

128
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,760
I'm having a headache
just by looking at it.

129
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,440
Just tell me the conclusion.

130
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,080
It's getting more and more costly.

131
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:44,960
Last year,

132
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,720
His Majesty spent as much as
the Chess of Generals Camp.

133
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,600
It means that

134
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,000
His Majesty's hunting expenses
for a year

135
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:53,200
can afford another
Chess of Generals Camp.

136
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,920
Cheng Xi used to serve the late emperor.

137
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,800
And the late emperor and His Majesty

138
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:03,800
are enemies.

139
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,760
His Majesty shouldn't have
spared Cheng Xi.

140
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,000
But not only he did that,

141
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,680
he trusted the Cheng siblings

142
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,520
with the Violet Bureau.

143
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:12,840
Why?

144
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,240
He wants to use the Violet Bureau

145
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,840
against the Chess of Generals Camp.

146
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:18,880
How can he do that?

147
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:19,840
With

148
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,160
those 36 maids?

149
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,200
So,

150
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,600
you suspect that

151
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,280
the girls who were sent away

152
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,680
are actually

153
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,600
being brought up by Qi Yan?

154
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,720
And the money comes from
his hunting trips?

155
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,240
I can't think of

156
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,120
another possibility except this.

157
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,480
I think

158
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,360
it's time for you to go back

159
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,480
and play chess with Sir.

160
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,920
I'm planning to do that.

161
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:47,750
(Duke Chu's Residence)

162
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,240
You want to...

163
00:07:58,440 --> 00:08:00,040
When I travelled with Qi Yan,

164
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,640
we ran into two assassination attempts.

165
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,400
And they were more like a provocation.

166
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,320
If we add your birthday banquet,

167
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,320
it'll be the third time.

168
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,440
What do you suspect?

169
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:10,960
The Violet Bureau

170
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,800
has been building forces in secret.

171
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,760
Someone found out about it

172
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,360
and wanted to use this chance
to make us fight.

173
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,320
So,

174
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,960
they sent a maid from Violet Bureau

175
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,080
to assassinate you

176
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,640
and frame it on Qi Yan.

177
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:24,720
Who is it?

178
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,360
I don't know that yet.

179
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,200
But since they purposely exposed

180
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,960
the secrets of Violet Bureau to us,

181
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,440
I'm sure they've planned out something.

182
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,880
I want to use Guan Wu's case

183
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,799
as a bait to uncover

184
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,320
this person's identity.

185
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:49,800
Your Majesty.

186
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,720
I have the answer.

187
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,040
Yu'er.

188
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:04,680
Get back.

189
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,280
Where's Yanzhi?

190
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,680
What answer do you have?

191
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,120
Yanzhi said that

192
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,400
when Zheng Wu and I entered the palace,

193
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,280
the ink in our Resumes

194
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,560
is different from others.

195
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:34,800
She suspects that
they have been tampered.

196
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,080
I've checked this

197
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,880
with Aunt.

198
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,040
They were damaged due to an accident.

199
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,080
Not forged.

200
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,200
What else?

201
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,520
What else?

202
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,960
Nothing else.

203
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:56,600
Let me ask you.

204
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,240
Why are you here?

205
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,360
Are you going to continue

206
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,960
investigating this together
with Qiu Yanzhi?

207
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,360
I want to continue
with this investigation.

208
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:09,120
But I don't plan to

209
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,320
join hands with Qiu Yanzhi.

210
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,480
I already said,

211
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,320
this case is closed.

212
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:40,920
It's not.

213
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,960
(Royal Repository)

214
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,720
What did you say?

215
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,080
I said,

216
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,800
this case is not closed.

217
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:58,360
Your Majesty,

218
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,920
Zheng Wu's revenge

219
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,320
is just the start.

220
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,160
During the Morning Dew Rebellion,

221
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,800
almost 1000 officials had been killed.

222
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,720
We had countless casualties.

223
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,720
Why won't you let me investigate?

224
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:09,760
What are you afraid of?

225
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,840
If I can't even find out

226
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,640
the identity of our enemies

227
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:16,880
and their purpose,

228
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,760
how can I protect you

229
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,800
with my sword?

230
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,400
For your safety

231
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:25,040
and to prevent the next assassination,

232
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:26,640
this is my duty

233
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:27,600
as the Sword Bearer.

234
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,120
I have to do this.

235
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,360
Yu'er!

236
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,480
Okay.

237
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,760
I'll tell you this then.

238
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:45,080
You are no longer the Sword Bearer.

239
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:48,800
Wait.

240
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:13,520
Cheng Huaizhi.

241
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:14,720
Yes, Your Majesty.

242
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:15,560
Pass down my decree.

243
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,840
Cheng Ruoyu will be removed from
her position as the Sword Bearer

244
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,680
and she's now just a commoner.

245
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,240
She'll leave the palace

246
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,240
and never come back.

247
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:27,760
Yes, Your Majesty.

248
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:29,720
Leave now.

249
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,120
Do you think I want this?

250
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:40,680
Yu'er.

251
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:03,440
Yu'er.

252
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,440
Wait.

253
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:05,680
The matron is still trying to help you.

254
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:07,280
This is not final.

255
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,360
Madam Li.

256
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,720
I've made up my mind.

257
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:11,040
No need to persuade me.

258
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:13,760
But where can you go

259
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,040
if you leave?

260
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,880
What about us?

261
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,840
Can you really abandon us?

262
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,360
I'm sorry that

263
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,560
I didn't live up to your expectation.

264
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,720
Before you became the Sword Bearer,

265
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,520
I was worried about you.

266
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,640
After you became the Sword Bearer,

267
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,240
I was even more anxious.

268
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:44,280
Now that you are not a Sword Bearer,

269
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,160
I'm still worried about you.

270
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:48,800
Aunt.

271
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,240
I'm sorry.

272
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,280
I've never wanted to

273
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,160
become a Sword Bearer.

274
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,720
I just want to be by your side.

275
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,640
Actually, this is not bad.

276
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,240
I've been kicked out from the palace.

277
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,120
But,

278
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,240
with my capabilities,

279
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,640
I can come back anytime.

280
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,240
So,

281
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,880
nothing will change.

282
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,240
Everything will be the same.

283
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:13,480
You.

284
00:14:14,160 --> 00:14:14,760
Forget it.

285
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,280
This is...

286
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:28,480
I didn't give you this because
I didn't want you to get into trouble.

287
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,000
But if I don't give it to you now,

