508
00:27:28,600 --> 00:27:29,280
I'm not asking you to drink.

509
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:30,280
I'm asking you to try.

510
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:31,480
I'm no longer

511
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,240
