526
00:29:09,280 --> 00:29:10,280
I was just being naughty

527
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:11,600
by adding water into the wine.

528
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:13,880
Those are for me.

529
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:17,040
Cheng Ruoyu.

530
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:19,400
Are you sure you want to commit treason?

531
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:26,320
Your Majesty.

532
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:28,560
Just tell me what you want.

533
00:29:28,760 --> 00:29:30,000
No need to beat around the bush.

534
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:35,680
