540
00:29:48,280 --> 00:29:49,120
You go against my decree.

541
00:29:49,240 --> 00:29:49,840
By kicking you out

542
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:50,640
instead of killing you,

543
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,520
it's already

544
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:53,920
