548
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:01,960
Or else,

549
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,400
I'll continue to investigate

550
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:04,600
Wu's case.

551
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:08,760
Cheng Ruoyu.

552
00:30:10,720 --> 00:30:11,520
Do you really think that

553
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:12,360
