00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:33,600
Very well.

562
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:36,720
With you being so weak,

563
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:37,760
I'm going to

564
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,960
